('Soup Recipes for Every Season', '20 nourishing soups from light to hearty.', 'Spring: pea, asparagus. Summer: gazpacho, corn chowder. Fall: butternut squash, minestrone. Winter: lentil, chicken noodle, beef stew. Techniques: roast vegetables first for depth, blend for creaminess, freeze individual portions, add fresh herbs at end.', 'article', 'recipes', ARRAY['soups', 'comfort food', 'seasonal cooking', 'meal prep'], true, 0),

('Breakfast Meal Prep: 10 Make-Ahead Options', 'Start your day right with prepped breakfasts.', 'Overnight oats variations, egg muffin cups, breakfast burritos, chia pudding, granola, breakfast cookies, frittata slices, yogurt parfait jars, baked oatmeal, protein pancakes. Most last 3-5 days refrigerated or freeze for longer storage.', 'article', 'recipes', ARRAY['breakfast', 'meal prep', 'make-ahead', 'morning meals'], true, 0),

('Buddha Bowls: 15 Balanced Bowl Recipes', 'Complete meals in a bowl with perfect balance.', 'Base: grain or greens. Add: protein, roasted vegetables, raw vegetables, healthy fat, sauce. Popular: Mediterranean, Mexican, Asian, Greek. Customize to preferences. Use leftovers creatively. Prep components ahead. Nutrition and flavor in every bite.', 'article', 'recipes', ARRAY['buddha bowls', 'grain bowls', 'balanced meals', 'lunch'], true, 0),

